WEBVTT

00:00:35.076 --> 00:00:36.536
So there was a boy and a girl.

00:00:36.619 --> 00:00:39.080
The girl was chasing that idiot boy.

00:00:39.164 --> 00:00:41.958
Then we were shocked when she suddenly
started shooting the man.

00:00:42.041 --> 00:00:44.043
It seems like Chiara
wanted to finish Mikoy.

00:00:44.127 --> 00:00:45.336
That's not how we see it.

00:00:45.420 --> 00:00:46.546
No, not really.

00:00:46.629 --> 00:00:48.590
What do you mean, "not really"?

00:00:48.673 --> 00:00:49.966
You're wrong about me.

00:00:50.049 --> 00:00:52.177
I'm still the same Mikoy you know.

00:00:55.597 --> 00:00:57.182
Maybe you just don't know me that well.

00:01:14.741 --> 00:01:16.743
And don't report this to anyone.

00:01:16.826 --> 00:01:18.036
Not even to Sianong.

00:01:18.119 --> 00:01:19.037
Actually, even before,

00:01:19.120 --> 00:01:21.581
I didn't really care who you were.

00:01:21.664 --> 00:01:24.042
I don't care about your past,
present, and future.

00:01:24.125 --> 00:01:25.960
Well, the truth is, I only want one thing.

00:01:26.044 --> 00:01:27.629
I just want to be with you.

00:01:34.552 --> 00:01:37.972
There's one more thing
you don't know about me.

00:01:39.057 --> 00:01:39.933
What is it?

00:01:40.016 --> 00:01:42.393
The thing about me is,

00:01:42.477 --> 00:01:44.604
I don't care

00:01:45.313 --> 00:01:47.190
whether it's forbidden or wrong.

00:01:48.399 --> 00:01:50.151
All I know is…

00:01:53.279 --> 00:01:55.657
I love you so much.

00:03:00.763 --> 00:03:02.473
You got allergies from that ramen?

00:03:02.557 --> 00:03:03.892
Yes, from the shrimp.

00:03:03.975 --> 00:03:05.018
But it's okay.

00:03:05.101 --> 00:03:06.686
I took anti-histamines.

00:04:14.545 --> 00:04:18.216
That's why you're speechless right now.

00:05:05.263 --> 00:05:06.264
Oh!

00:05:08.391 --> 00:05:10.018
Oh, sir, ma'am is really stressed.

00:05:10.101 --> 00:05:13.521
She told me to stand by
in case you get stressed too.

00:05:15.064 --> 00:05:16.524
Wow!

00:05:21.988 --> 00:05:24.115
Sorry, sir, I was just following orders.

00:05:34.709 --> 00:05:35.752
Of course, sir.

00:05:35.835 --> 00:05:37.670
I signed an NDA, anyway.

00:05:58.316 --> 00:05:59.484
Why are you laughing?

00:05:59.567 --> 00:06:01.110
You're laughing too.

00:06:01.194 --> 00:06:02.528
Because you're laughing.

00:06:17.210 --> 00:06:18.461
Exactly.

00:06:22.799 --> 00:06:28.763
Well, now I know
why they call you "blessed".

00:06:46.572 --> 00:06:48.616
Can we just stay here for now?

00:06:51.702 --> 00:06:53.121
I don't want to leave anymore.

00:06:55.498 --> 00:06:57.333
I don't want to go out into the world.

00:07:01.170 --> 00:07:02.380
Mikoy.

00:07:06.676 --> 00:07:07.760
You know,

00:07:07.844 --> 00:07:10.471
I wish I had superpowers.

00:07:11.097 --> 00:07:13.057
So I could stop the world.

00:07:15.268 --> 00:07:17.478
Because what matters to me is…

00:07:20.731 --> 00:07:21.566
this.

00:07:26.779 --> 00:07:28.072
You.

00:07:29.657 --> 00:07:30.783
Me.

00:07:33.244 --> 00:07:34.662
Just the two of us.

00:07:38.916 --> 00:07:40.084
You know that?

00:07:48.801 --> 00:07:51.012
We have each other anyway.

00:07:53.306 --> 00:07:55.766
If you're not ready to face the world yet,

00:07:57.393 --> 00:07:59.645
we can run away from it.

00:08:02.565 --> 00:08:03.566
How?

00:09:53.634 --> 00:09:55.261
Okay, I'm here now.

00:10:02.727 --> 00:10:04.812
Are you in a bad mood again?

00:10:04.895 --> 00:10:06.814
What took you so long?

00:10:07.398 --> 00:10:10.234
The restaurant has been open
for a while, but the kitchen

00:10:10.318 --> 00:10:12.820
is still closed because
the ingredients aren't here yet.

00:10:12.903 --> 00:10:15.197
There were so many people
at the market, love.

00:10:15.990 --> 00:10:17.158
I thought it was Christmas.

00:10:17.241 --> 00:10:19.285
Just admit it.

00:10:19.368 --> 00:10:21.287
You were fooling around again!

00:10:22.288 --> 00:10:23.414
Come on, now.

00:10:24.415 --> 00:10:25.625
Don't be mad, love.

00:10:27.084 --> 00:10:28.794
Getting angry this early in the morning?

00:10:29.754 --> 00:10:31.505
Someone might see us later

00:10:31.589 --> 00:10:34.216
and say again that you're not
getting enough affection.

00:10:34.300 --> 00:10:35.134
Come here.

00:10:35.217 --> 00:10:36.135
Oh, come on!

00:10:38.137 --> 00:10:39.889
Let go of me!

00:10:39.972 --> 00:10:40.890
Come on!

00:10:40.973 --> 00:10:42.516
Just start prepping!

00:10:42.600 --> 00:10:44.101
You're so extra.

00:10:44.185 --> 00:10:47.355
You don't have to win me over
with all your sweetness.

00:10:47.438 --> 00:10:48.689
I already love you, okay?

00:10:48.773 --> 00:10:50.358
You know that I love you so much.

00:10:50.441 --> 00:10:51.859
So you don't need to make me swoon.

00:10:51.942 --> 00:10:54.654
You have a lot of fan service.

00:10:54.737 --> 00:10:56.197
You know, sweetheart.

00:10:56.280 --> 00:10:57.740
You still need to be sweet.

00:10:57.823 --> 00:11:01.243
Because love needs to be nurtured, okay?

00:11:02.662 --> 00:11:04.497
So it won't wither

00:11:04.580 --> 00:11:07.124
and can continue to grow and flourish.

00:11:07.750 --> 00:11:08.918
Right?

00:11:09.001 --> 00:11:10.461
We're late.

00:11:10.544 --> 00:11:12.922
I told you we're already late.

00:11:13.005 --> 00:11:14.799
-Come on!
-Dasho!

00:11:15.674 --> 00:11:17.510
Are you two flirting?

00:11:17.593 --> 00:11:18.761
Huh?

00:11:23.015 --> 00:11:24.141
Huh?

00:11:29.105 --> 00:11:30.940
Okay, sorry, ma'am.

00:11:31.023 --> 00:11:32.733
It's just a joke.

00:12:11.981 --> 00:12:14.108
-Team fight!
-Team fight!

00:12:20.406 --> 00:12:21.365
Hiyaah!

00:12:21.449 --> 00:12:23.409
-Come on. Go get ready.
-Oh, right, I was just joking.

00:12:23.492 --> 00:12:25.411
-Now look, we're going to be even later.
-Oh, right.

00:12:46.765 --> 00:12:48.934
Oh, stop daydreaming.
We're already late, aren't we?

00:12:49.018 --> 00:12:50.686
We're late because of you, right?

00:12:50.769 --> 00:12:52.563
-Is that so?
-Yes.

00:12:52.646 --> 00:12:54.064
-Really?
-Yes.

00:12:54.148 --> 00:12:55.649
Because this person here…

00:12:55.733 --> 00:12:57.276
-Who is it?
-It's…

00:12:57.359 --> 00:12:58.194
-Chao Ting!
-Who?

00:12:58.277 --> 00:12:59.653
Out there, being so annoying.

00:12:59.737 --> 00:13:00.571
Why?

00:13:00.654 --> 00:13:01.864
I don't know.

00:13:03.365 --> 00:13:04.492
Ouch, why?

00:13:04.575 --> 00:13:06.285
Come on. Stop fooling around.

00:13:06.368 --> 00:13:07.703
It's you!

00:13:07.786 --> 00:13:10.247
I'm not even doing anything.
I'm cooking here. Can't you see?

00:13:10.331 --> 00:13:11.957
I don't know about you.

00:13:12.041 --> 00:13:13.626
My mustache keep falling off
because of you.

00:13:56.168 --> 00:13:57.378
Of course, there's no problem.

00:13:57.461 --> 00:13:58.879
Are you sure?

00:14:07.680 --> 00:14:08.681
Anyway,

00:14:08.764 --> 00:14:11.976
I just came here because
everything is ready.

00:14:22.111 --> 00:14:24.321
It's a good thing we're all here today.

00:14:24.405 --> 00:14:25.656
I just want to align everyone

00:14:25.739 --> 00:14:28.158
on what's been happening
with the Moravianos.

00:14:28.701 --> 00:14:30.035
For the past few months,

00:14:30.119 --> 00:14:32.580
we've seen no movement
from the Moravianos.

00:14:37.293 --> 00:14:41.672
So that means
they've halted their illegal operations.

00:14:55.185 --> 00:14:57.980
Because he suddenly disappeared.

00:14:59.023 --> 00:15:01.609
Without even saying goodbye. Boom!

00:15:01.692 --> 00:15:02.818
Just gone.

00:15:17.207 --> 00:15:20.336
But the end point is,

00:15:20.419 --> 00:15:22.129
they escaped together.

00:15:34.725 --> 00:15:36.936
Maybe Chiara doesn't want
that life anymore.

00:15:55.996 --> 00:15:57.498
Which means,

00:15:58.082 --> 00:15:59.208
starting today,

00:15:59.875 --> 00:16:05.297
Mikoy is now considered
an enemy of the state.

00:16:18.435 --> 00:16:20.479
You know what this means.

00:16:20.562 --> 00:16:24.692
This is basically a shoot-to-kill order
in the eyes of covert operators.

00:16:30.614 --> 00:16:34.576
But you know our law enforcement
operatives in this country.

00:16:37.371 --> 00:16:39.331
And you're putting Mikoy's life at risk.

00:16:39.415 --> 00:16:43.127
I didn't put Mikoy's life in danger.

00:16:49.341 --> 00:16:52.136
Maybe Mikoy had a reason for doing that.

00:16:56.515 --> 00:16:58.100
He's crazy in love,

00:16:58.183 --> 00:17:01.311
and it looks like he's being manipulated
by the Valtrovi daughter.

00:17:02.271 --> 00:17:04.023
He has contributed a lot to the agency.

00:17:08.360 --> 00:17:12.656
I should've listened to Sianong
when he said Mikoy is compromised.

00:17:12.740 --> 00:17:16.201
Then maybe we wouldn't have
ended up in this situation.

00:17:17.244 --> 00:17:18.287
Sir, maybe--

00:17:20.789 --> 00:17:23.709
Don't tell me
you're taking Alex's side now?

00:18:19.348 --> 00:18:20.516
Wow!

00:18:38.700 --> 00:18:42.037
It's not just that our asset disappeared.

00:18:52.548 --> 00:18:54.216
Now we can't penetrate it anymore.

00:18:54.299 --> 00:18:58.595
We can't even file a case
against Viktor and Donabel.

00:19:17.406 --> 00:19:19.283
He's not even active on social media.

00:19:20.784 --> 00:19:23.245
We don't even know if he's still alive.

00:19:23.328 --> 00:19:24.246
He's alive.

00:19:30.836 --> 00:19:34.006
For all I know, he could be spilling
all of the agency's secrets

00:19:34.089 --> 00:19:35.549
and selling them!

00:20:38.028 --> 00:20:40.989
But he had better have a good explanation

00:20:41.073 --> 00:20:43.825
why he ran away with that Valtrovi girl.

00:20:52.000 --> 00:20:53.043
Because if not,

00:20:54.378 --> 00:20:56.672
I will personally have him imprisoned.

00:20:58.757 --> 00:21:01.343
Yes, sir. I'll find Mikoy
and bring him back here.

00:21:24.783 --> 00:21:26.368
Why are you spacing out?

00:21:30.372 --> 00:21:33.166
Nothing. I was just wondering why

00:21:33.250 --> 00:21:35.711
she called us rice cookers while ago.

00:21:40.507 --> 00:21:41.550
Is that it?

00:21:42.175 --> 00:21:44.136
Gosh! That's all?

00:21:44.219 --> 00:21:46.263
I thought it was something serious.

00:21:46.972 --> 00:21:50.934
Well, maybe she called us
her rice cookers because

00:21:51.018 --> 00:21:53.937
we can handle the pressure in her kitchen?

00:21:54.896 --> 00:21:55.897
Is that so?

00:21:55.981 --> 00:21:58.025
Then she should've called us
pressure cookers.

00:21:58.108 --> 00:22:00.819
Those can handle more pressure
than rice cookers, right?

00:22:02.612 --> 00:22:03.905
You're right.

00:22:08.994 --> 00:22:13.040
Is that what was bothering you earlier?
Is that why you were late?

00:22:17.002 --> 00:22:19.254
Tell me. Why were you late earlier?

00:22:27.179 --> 00:22:28.513
Come on, Mikoy.

00:22:31.516 --> 00:22:33.101
You can't take a different route.

00:22:33.185 --> 00:22:35.312
We have to stick to the same routine.

00:22:36.396 --> 00:22:38.273
Otherwise, you'll stand out.

00:22:40.942 --> 00:22:43.487
You should already be in the kitchen
before rush hour, right?

00:22:43.570 --> 00:22:45.947
Because more people showing up
means more eyes.

00:22:46.031 --> 00:22:48.658
We don't know who might spot you.

00:22:50.619 --> 00:22:52.662
Our movements have to be predictable.

00:22:52.746 --> 00:22:55.165
So we know what's safe and what's not.

00:23:03.048 --> 00:23:04.883
May I explain now?

00:23:09.429 --> 00:23:12.057
I just had to stop somewhere earlier.

00:23:12.974 --> 00:23:14.726
What else could you possibly need to do?

00:23:16.478 --> 00:23:17.604
This.

00:23:21.149 --> 00:23:22.317
What's that?

00:23:40.168 --> 00:23:42.212
-You, I swear!
-Ouch.

00:23:42.295 --> 00:23:43.547
You're so annoying.

00:23:43.630 --> 00:23:46.341
You always have to make me mad
before making me swoon.

00:23:46.424 --> 00:23:47.717
Of course!

00:23:48.343 --> 00:23:50.262
It makes things more exciting, right?

00:23:52.514 --> 00:23:53.640
Right?

00:24:21.001 --> 00:24:23.420
You have no idea how happy I am.

00:25:07.505 --> 00:25:09.633
Do you miss Mom and Dad?

00:25:09.716 --> 00:25:10.717
Angelito?

00:25:10.800 --> 00:25:12.886
The simple bakery of Pinagpala?

00:25:17.682 --> 00:25:18.767
I can't calm down.

00:25:22.896 --> 00:25:24.564
She's trusting you.

00:25:24.648 --> 00:25:27.984
Oh, dear, this should stay
between us. Okay?

00:25:28.068 --> 00:25:32.864
But our friends are on high alert here

00:25:32.948 --> 00:25:36.284
because a lot of people
are roaming around!

00:25:36.368 --> 00:25:37.744
Why are you looking for Mikoy?

00:25:48.880 --> 00:25:50.715
There's a possible way for that.

00:25:50.799 --> 00:25:52.300
We should show ourselves to them.

00:25:52.384 --> 00:25:56.930
The one to reach out, face it,
and be humane. Just like that.